<section class="story" id="story">
  <div class="container story__inner">
    <div class="story__left">
      <div class="section-num">01</div>
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Who we are</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">A community for Muslim women. And a place to find a Quran teacher you can trust.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="story__body">
      <p>
        Laha Space started because finding the right Quran teacher online is genuinely hard. You search, you try someone, something feels off, and slowly you stop. We have seen it happen too many times.
      </p>
      <p>
        So we built something different. Every teacher here is a woman who has been personally interviewed, put through a teaching test, and reviewed by our team before her name ever appears on this page. Not because we wanted to make it hard to join, but because the women learning here deserve that certainty.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are looking for a teacher you can actually trust, you are in the right place.
      </p>
      <p class="story__signature">— The Laha Space team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="vetting" id="vetting">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="vetting__head">
      <div class="section-num">02</div>
      <div>
        <span class="section-eyebrow">How we choose our teachers</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Seven stages.<br/><em>No shortcuts.</em></h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Every teacher you see here has passed through our full vetting process. Here is exactly what that means.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vetting__body">

      <div class="vetting__sidebar">
        <div class="vetting__progress-track">
          <div class="vetting__progress-fill" id="vettingProgress"></div>
        </div>
        <ol class="vetting__nav" id="vettingNav">
          <li class="vnav__item vnav__item--active" data-stage="0">
            <span class="vnav__num">01</span>
            <span class="vnav__label">Application</span>
          </li>
          <li class="vnav__item" data-stage="1">
            <span class="vnav__num">02</span>
            <span class="vnav__label">Screening</span>
          </li>
          <li class="vnav__item" data-stage="2">
            <span class="vnav__num">03</span>
            <span class="vnav__label">Interview</span>
          </li>
          <li class="vnav__item" data-stage="3">
            <span class="vnav__num">04</span>
            <span class="vnav__label">Review</span>
          </li>
          <li class="vnav__item" data-stage="4">
            <span class="vnav__num">05</span>
            <span class="vnav__label">Teaching test</span>
          </li>
          <li class="vnav__item" data-stage="5">
            <span class="vnav__num">06</span>
            <span class="vnav__label">Training</span>
          </li>
          <li class="vnav__item" data-stage="6">
            <span class="vnav__num">07</span>
            <span class="vnav__label">Live listing</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <ol class="vetting__cards" id="vettingCards">
        <li class="vcard" data-index="0">
          <span class="vcard__num">01</span>
          <h4 class="vcard__title">Application</h4>
          <p class="vcard__desc">The teacher submits a detailed application covering her qualifications, ijazah, teaching experience and references. Nothing moves forward until the full picture is clear.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="vcard" data-index="1">
          <span class="vcard__num">02</span>
          <h4 class="vcard__title">Initial screening</h4>
          <p class="vcard__desc">Our team goes through every document submitted. If anything is missing or unclear, we follow up before proceeding.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="vcard" data-index="2">
          <span class="vcard__num">03</span>
          <h4 class="vcard__title">One on one interview</h4>
          <p class="vcard__desc">A personal conversation with the teacher to understand her background, her approach to teaching and her values. This is not a formality.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="vcard" data-index="3">
          <span class="vcard__num">04</span>
          <h4 class="vcard__title">Interview review</h4>
          <p class="vcard__desc">The team reviews everything from the interview together before deciding whether to proceed to the teaching test.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="vcard" data-index="4">
          <span class="vcard__num">05</span>
          <h4 class="vcard__title">Teaching test</h4>
          <p class="vcard__desc">The teacher delivers a live teaching demonstration. Our team observes, takes notes and evaluates how she actually teaches, not just what she knows.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="vcard" data-index="5">
          <span class="vcard__num">06</span>
          <h4 class="vcard__title">Training program</h4>
          <p class="vcard__desc">Accepted teachers complete our internal onboarding program before going live. This ensures every teacher in this space meets the same standard.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="vcard vcard--final" data-index="6">
          <span class="vcard__num">07</span>
          <h4 class="vcard__title">Live listing <span class="stage__pill">live</span></h4>
          <p class="vcard__desc">Only now does the teacher appear on Laha Space. Every profile you see here has cleared all seven stages. No exceptions.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="teachers-section" id="teachers">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="teachers-section__head">
