          Laha Space is a community first. Beyond the teacher listing, there is a WhatsApp group, workshops, and a growing space where Muslim women come together to learn, support one another, and connect. If you are looking for more than just a teacher, you are welcome here.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="pill pill--solid">
          <span>Join the community</span>
          <span class="pill__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="apply-cta" data-aos="fade-up">
